<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I got this mask when i first ventured to kunark as a 27 cleric, because i had nothing but a banded mask at the time i gladly equiped the mask for a more favorible ac 5, i still wear it today when i am a 35th cleric, i just haven't gotten around to purchasing a plat ruby vail yet. =)  I think the negative cha. is just a great think to tell people who havent heard of the mask before and ask the stats "its 5 ac and -25 cha kid".  I keep up hope that maybe, one day this may be involved in some sorta quest to turn that -25 cha into +25 cha, and that no one has figured it out yet. =P Good for newbies with out a mask. Goodbye.</font></td></tr></table>
